  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Click one row in the customer list.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 2.026,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "That single click opens the whole member.",
      "startS": 2.68,
      "endS": 5.156,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "Everything you need for most tickets is now on one page:",
      "startS": 5.415,
      "endS": 8.702,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "who they are up top, their numbers just below, and the detail waiting in the tabs.",
      "startS": 8.988,
      "endS": 13.704,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "Start at the top and work down.",
      "startS": 13.982,
      "endS": 15.678,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "Look at the header.",
      "startS": 16.153,
      "endS": 17.151,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "The avatar, the name, the plan badge, and the line beneath it tell you four things at a glance:",
      "startS": 17.462,
      "endS": 23.217,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "who you have, what they pay for, where they wash, and whether the account is in good standing.",
      "startS": 23.726,
      "endS": 24.36,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "Read that line first on every call.",
      "startS": 24.699,
      "endS": 26.837,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "It confirms you are on the right person.",
      "startS": 27.172,
      "endS": 34.145,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "Now the chips under the name.",
      "startS": 34.555,
      "endS": 36.272,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Plan active, a plate on file for the cameras, auto-pay running, texting turned on.",
      "startS": 37.125,
      "endS": 40.121,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "Four little flags that answer half the \"is my account set up right\" questions",
      "startS": 40.552,
      "endS": 43.15,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "before you open a single tab.",
      "startS": 43.708,
      "endS": 50.32,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "Over on the right, four controls.",
      "startS": 50.771,
      "endS": 51.694,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "Back returns you to the list.",
      "startS": 51.977,
      "endS": 52.995,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "Edit Customer opens the form we cover next lesson.",
      "startS": 53.308,
      "endS": 54.852,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "Actions holds the member-level moves, and we open that at the end.",
      "startS": 55.37,
      "endS": 58.333,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "The one you never touch is Delete.",
      "startS": 58.751,
      "endS": 64.96,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "Under the header sits a strip of six numbers.",
      "startS": 65.426,
      "endS": 68.325,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "Think of it as the account's vital signs:",
      "startS": 69.088,
      "endS": 71.211,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "when they joined, what they spend, how often they come, their points, the next renewal,",
      "startS": 71.608,
      "endS": 73.533,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "and the last time you saw them.",
      "startS": 73.779,
      "endS": 77.087,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "When a member asks \"how long have I been with you\" or \"when do I renew,\"",
      "startS": 77.329,
      "endS": 78.886,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "the answer is right here, no digging.",
      "startS": 79.704,
      "endS": 87.2,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "Below that, a row of shortcuts.",
      "startS": 87.596,
      "endS": 89.558,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Each chip is a doorway into one slice of the account:",
      "startS": 90.224,
      "endS": 93.147,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "their vehicles, their tickets, their wash books, gift cards, house account, loyalty, rewards.",
      "startS": 93.58,
      "endS": 99.869,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "Instead of hunting, you click straight through to the part you need.",
      "startS": 100.628,
      "endS": 103.52,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "The Overview tab opens first.",
      "startS": 103.976,
      "endS": 105.887,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "Up top, an A-I snapshot writes the account in plain language,",
      "startS": 106.422,
      "endS": 112.582,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "with a Regenerate button to refresh it.",
      "startS": 113.346,
      "endS": 114.53,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "Below are the charts: visits by month, the mix of services, spend over time, and points.",
      "startS": 114.96,
      "endS": 115.908,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "Treat the snapshot as a helpful draft you confirm against the real tabs,",
      "startS": 116.235,
      "endS": 119.764,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "the same rule you use for Shyne.",
      "startS": 120.754,
      "endS": 126.529,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "Switch to Contact.",
      "startS": 126.96,
      "endS": 128.133,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "This is the record itself: name and business details, address, phone and email,",
      "startS": 128.796,
      "endS": 130.212,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "plus the notification and consent settings.",
      "startS": 130.88,
      "endS": 132.557,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "You read it here; you change it on the edit form in the next lesson.",
      "startS": 133.029,
      "endS": 135.006,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "For now it answers \"is our contact info current.\"",
      "startS": 135.464,
      "endS": 145.63,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "Open Membership. This is the one you will use most.",
      "startS": 146.138,
      "endS": 147.148,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "Plan details, the loyalty section with the bar code,",
      "startS": 147.417,
      "endS": 149.229,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "the visit and spend totals, and the billing cycle.",
      "startS": 149.669,
      "endS": 152.731,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "Two fields earn their keep here.",
      "startS": 153.069,
      "endS": 156.039,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "The bar code is exactly what the POS scans, so this is your first stop when a tag will not read.",
      "startS": 156.543,
      "endS": 164.107,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "And next charge tells the member when they get billed again.",
      "startS": 164.536,
      "endS": 167.895,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "Now Payments.",
      "startS": 168.305,
      "endS": 169.524,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "The cards on file and any prepaid credit live here.",
      "startS": 170.24,
      "endS": 173.403,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "You can see what is set up to bill, and you can see remaining book value.",
      "startS": 174.002,
      "endS": 177.583,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "Reading it is safe.",
      "startS": 177.838,
      "endS": 178.87,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "Adding a card is not part of this walk.",
      "startS": 179.214,
      "endS": 181.302,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "Last tab in Part 1, Vehicles.",
      "startS": 181.76,
      "endS": 184.149,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "These are the plates the cameras match to the plan.",
      "startS": 184.77,
      "endS": 187.217,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "You will also see a re-tracts list, the equipment holds set on this account's washes,",
      "startS": 187.725,
      "endS": 189.828,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "like a skipped tire shine or top brush.",
      "startS": 190.16,
      "endS": 192.521,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "When a member says the wash left something off, this is where you check.",
      "startS": 192.904,
      "endS": 199.459,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "Linked Accounts.",
      "startS": 199.92,
      "endS": 200.556,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p58",
      "text": "Shared plans and household members show up here:",
      "startS": 200.556,
      "endS": 203.564,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p59",
      "text": "a spouse on the same membership, a second driver, a family link.",
      "startS": 203.564,
      "endS": 207.948,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p60",
      "text": "When one person is asking about another's plan,",
      "startS": 207.948,
      "endS": 211.06,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p61",
      "text": "check this tab before you assume they are separate accounts.",
      "startS": 211.06,
      "endS": 214.24,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p62",
      "text": "Activity is the running log.",
      "startS": 214.743,
      "endS": 216.844,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p63",
      "text": "Every visit and transaction, newest first, each with a type, a date, and an amount.",
      "startS": 217.167,
      "endS": 220.11,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p64",
      "text": "When you need \"what happened and when,\"",
      "startS": 220.323,
      "endS": 223.003,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p65",
      "text": "you scroll this instead of piecing it together from tickets.",
      "startS": 223.275,
      "endS": 228.96,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p66",
      "text": "Open Messaging.",
      "startS": 229.36,
      "endS": 230.419,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p67",
      "text": "This is the two-way text thread with the member, and it shows whether they opted in.",
      "startS": 231.045,
      "endS": 235.169,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p68",
      "text": "Read it to see what was already said, so you are not repeating a message someone sent yesterday.",
      "startS": 235.652,
      "endS": 240.284,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p69",
      "text": "One hard rule: you never send from here in the demo.",
      "startS": 241.034,
      "endS": 242.134,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p70",
      "text": "Read only.",
      "startS": 242.544,
      "endS": 245.84,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p71",
      "text": "Now Notes.",
      "startS": 246.24,
      "endS": 247.068,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p72",
      "text": "These are internal staff notes, and the label says it plainly: not visible to the customer.",
      "startS": 247.546,
      "endS": 250.85,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p73",
      "text": "Below them, the full communication history by channel, and a change log.",
      "startS": 251.19,
      "endS": 252.715,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p74",
      "text": "This is where you leave context for the next agent",
      "startS": 253.411,
      "endS": 257.554,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p75",
      "text": "and where you find what a teammate already did.",
      "startS": 258.249,
      "endS": 260.694,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p76",
      "text": "Save Note stays untouched today.",
      "startS": 261.047,
      "endS": 266.243,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p77",
      "text": "Finally, open Actions.",
      "startS": 266.72,
      "endS": 268.429,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p78",
      "text": "Two items today: Issue Wash and Refund Customer.",
      "startS": 269.589,
      "endS": 270.495,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p79",
      "text": "The old guide listed six, so if you are expecting Cancel or Pause here and they are missing,",
      "startS": 270.959,
      "endS": 273.443,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p80",
      "text": "that gap is logged and parked, not something you broke.",
      "startS": 273.996,
      "endS": 282.705,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p81",
      "text": "Read the list, then close it.",
      "startS": 283.377,
      "endS": 285.02,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p82",
      "text": "Both of these move money or issue value, so in the demo you open the menu and stop.",
      "startS": 285.521,
      "endS": 290.32,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p83",
      "text": "That is the whole record.",
      "startS": 290.72,
      "endS": 292.279,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p84",
      "text": "Header and chips tell you who.",
      "startS": 292.864,
      "endS": 294.806,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p85",
      "text": "The metric strip gives the headline numbers.",
      "startS": 295.444,
      "endS": 297.712,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p86",
      "text": "The chips jump you into any slice.",
      "startS": 298.021,
      "endS": 300.35,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p87",
      "text": "And nine tabs answer the everyday tickets:",
      "startS": 300.606,
      "endS": 303.177,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p88",
      "text": "the bar code and the next charge on Membership,",
      "startS": 303.493,
      "endS": 305.812,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p89",
      "text": "consent on Contact and Messaging, the internal trail on Notes.",
      "startS": 306.071,
      "endS": 310.052,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p90",
      "text": "One page, read top to bottom, and you changed nothing to get every answer.",
      "startS": 310.644,
      "endS": 315.231,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}